      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's... a pretty heavy way to put it. You think I'm a burden? I don't even know anyone well enough to be a burden to. I just feel so invisible. Like, if I just stopped showing up, if I just turned everything off and never came back... would anyone even stop to wonder where I went? Or would it just be more silence?",
